data.title: Biba Singh and Dipps Bhamrah bring you "Panga Facebook Da"
data.meta_description: New York based Doctor and singer Biba Singh is just released her first ever Bhangra collaboration with UK based producer Dipps Bhamrah titled “Panga
data.text:
New York based Doctor and singer Biba Singh is just released her first ever Bhangra collaboration with UK based producer Dipps Bhamrah titled “Panga Facebook Da.” Check out this fun track!

Biba Singh has collaborated with one of UK’s finest Djs and Music Producers for this track, Dipps Bhamrah has been responsible for some smash hit anthems through his career. He’s not only a talented DJ but also hosts his own Punjabi show on the BBC Asian Network which strengthens his knowledge for music and the Punjabi scene. “Panga Facebook Da” is a song every couple will relate to! It’s through and through Bhangra which will be one of the favorites for the dance offs! It’s funny quirky lyrics by Amrit Mangwalia reflect the funny stresses of Facebook in your relationships and the renowned Video director- Raju Sethi has conceptualized the music video wonderfully.

The song has been signed to UK based record label Generasian Records which is owned by the international Dj and producer Dipps Bhamrah he’s excited to release this international project,

“Biba is a talented singer, she’s got a different vibe. We have kept the track catchy and fun, it’s got that UK Bhangra feel to it. This song’s vision, concept and storyline was designed by renowned PR Guru Nisha Sahdev”.

Biba Singh,has a number of successful releases in the past including “Nachne da Cha” and “Akhian” released by moviebox and is now looking to hit the international market. She is working on a single with DJ Shadow of Dubai and Taz of stereonation and shooting her next music video as we speak! Be sure to keep it locked on Urban Asian for more updates on Biba!
